sentences: He holds his PhD in art studies from Tehran University and now he is Professor and Maestro at Tehran University of Art, University of Tehran, and Islamic Azad University and teaches several courses such as: Santour, Sight Reading, History of music, Stage Performance, Orchestration, Organology, Analysis of music, Philosophy of Music and Music Theory at the levels of bachelors and master's degree.
